Ali ti ne sanjaš ništa.

00:37:35.333 --> 00:37:38.333
Već Skarlet.

00:38:58.417 --> 00:39:00.417
Sjedi.

00:39:11.625 --> 00:39:15.292
Jesi li dobro, dušo?

00:39:16.875 --> 00:39:20.300
Danas imam toliko posla.

00:39:20.500 --> 00:39:25.921
<i>Moram kupiti Izabeli poklon, a
onda na manikir i pedikir.</i>

00:39:26.121 --> 00:39:31.542
<i>Zabrljali su termin pa
moram doći u 04:30, ali...</i>

00:39:37.500 --> 00:39:39.708
To je sve.

00:39:58.292 --> 00:40:01.917
<i>Hoćeš li otvoriti, dušo?</i>

00:40:09.000 --> 00:40:14.958
