00:40:40.625 --> 00:40:43.917
Šta se dešava?
Jesi li dobro?

00:40:44.117 --> 00:40:46.967
Pejdž, je li mu dobro?

00:40:47.167 --> 00:40:50.500
Daj, čovječe,
samo pokušavam...

00:41:08.250 --> 00:41:10.250
Aleks?

00:41:12.958 --> 00:41:16.625
Šta radiš?
Dođi u krevet.

00:41:21.750 --> 00:41:24.000
<i>Vrijeme je za prognozu...</i>

00:41:31.708 --> 00:41:34.042
Polako.

00:41:35.042 --> 00:41:38.625
Hoćeš da te oraspoložim?

00:41:38.750 --> 00:41:41.500
Opusti se.

00:41:44.875 --> 00:41:49.875
Zaboravi na sve drugo.
- Kako to misliš na sve drugo?

00:42:01.250 --> 00:42:05.042
