Pejdž?

00:58:18.042 --> 00:58:19.958
Aleks?

00:58:23.542 --> 00:58:25.667
Aleks.

00:58:27.833 --> 00:58:30.917
Šta se dešava?

00:58:37.250 --> 00:58:39.250
Ne znam.

00:58:40.167 --> 00:58:43.167
Jesi li dobro?

00:58:43.542 --> 00:58:45.583
Jesi li dobro?

00:58:47.958 --> 00:58:52.275
Ne.
